cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a deep learning method, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as well. Additionally, the paper deals with multi-task learning, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also mentions unsupervised learning, which could suggest cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with security and surveillance, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
